    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>A simpler way would be ...</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$key</span> = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">array_column</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$blogusers</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'display_name'</span>);
<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">array_multisort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$key</span>, SORT_ASC, <span class="hljs-variable">$blogusers</span>]

<span class="hljs-keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$blogusers</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$bloguser</span>) ...
</code></pre>
    </div>
