    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Take a look at following article. It does describe how to use <code>usort()</code> and also describes how to use <code>create_function()</code> so that you can use single function to sort on different fields (with required direction <code>asc</code> or <code>desc</code>).</p>

<p><a href="http://phpave.com/sorting-associative-array-specific-key/" rel="nofollow noreferrer">http://phpave.com/sorting-associative-array-specific-key/</a></p>
    </div>
